{"tid":663272,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"三月我去了意大利睇波和食放題","createTime":"2018-05-13T07:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:44:30.000Z","uid":60435,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa52e4029ce8c7d45d7143babfded9393fc99ce","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"有無人想睇？有我就繼續講"},{"pid":"60f7dad93456fe2a5ae1b3398ebd43622864179b","tid":663272,"uid":137755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"講啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86314fef153deb2fe475d3e59820cf29a61e57b","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"序<br />\n<br />\n講下笑姐<br />\n我點都會繼續講<br />\n話說自從三年前同完個蛆friend（我是米蘭fan）去完意大利<br />\n一直念念不忘<br />\n決定2X歲前再一個人去<br />\n於是就買左機票阿聯油4875$（米蘭入巴黎走）嘅機票<br />\n過返個生日之旅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人去秦國台灣就試過<br />\n歐洲真係未試過<br />\n但我又唔驚嘅<br />\n因為我真係好撚鐘意意大利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但巴黎 啲人講到咁危險<br />\n我都係去探朋友有人照住所以就去埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5977f6210618fc28f09dc7f821d7d6cc5a0fa9ce","tid":663272,"uid":45164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去咗幾耐同洗咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4308e7ec07106c72580c03004182087b23ba2f6","tid":663272,"uid":61363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"留明<br />\n我都想去睇祖記<br />\n但係都靈好似係冷門城市嚟？"},{"pid":"a2f2c9c3ef3d3978850179a00c91f021d49cdeb1","tid":663272,"uid":18005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"睇咗做和波放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fe1f75214bf35723b30686c8a2306eb9b24fec","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去咗幾耐同洗咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n意大利 十二日<br />\n法國 四日<br />\n萬幾蚊"},{"pid":"ecdfe04ed5cd3120774acef77ee21b9154f90062","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇咗做和波放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n米蘭緊係睇後防放題"},{"pid":"b5766420976541693e7e3e48a125627107e470f0","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明<br />\n我都想去睇祖記<br />\n但係都靈好似係冷門城市嚟？</blockquote><br />\n都算冷門<br />\n但啲人好好"},{"pid":"897a59b5662859fab3158e1ea2edab087b413971","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"講返正題<br />\n由於上次已經去了熱門地方：<br />\n五漁村 米蘭 威尼斯 佛羅倫斯 都靈<br />\n（喺舊登開過post 但講睇波講太多爛左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\nbtw我雖然窮遊，但我都有要求的，我要求就係要坐中東機，唔一定是三寶，但一定要中東轉機。我很喜歡中東文化，上次坐了Qatar，今次咁岩Emirates有特價，我很快手就買了機票，$4572 （更正）米蘭入巴黎出。行程方面，我現在簡介一下：米蘭-Bolzano-維羅納-博洛尼亞-巴黎 揀博洛尼亞完全係因為這裡去巴黎嘅機票較便宜。至於住宿，主要以便宜airbnb為主，本身book了三間hostel，後尾有啲顧慮（遲啲講），所以book返airbnb，有的是租一間房，有的是租一間屋。交通除左去巴黎，都是用腳同火車為主，其實本來我book了巴士，但後來嬲左巴士公司，所以都取消了。（遲啲講）"},{"pid":"09cab0ce01c2ae2e353663ba5265a0b93f1797f0","tid":663272,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12fe1f75214bf35723b30686c8a2306eb9b24fec","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去咗幾耐同洗咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n意大利 十二日<br />\n法國 四日<br />\n萬幾蚊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"睇場波都千幾蚊<br />\n萬零蚊十幾日<br />\n好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8d8f20ca96abc4fa2ef6b33d5460bc69ef067b","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"（一）旅程正式開始<br />\n<br />\n第一日-搭飛機 2/3<br />\n我從香港國際機場出發，首先乘坐阿聯酋航空A380 前往杜拜，一上機，嘩好靚，好大，咁大個女第一次坐阿聯酋，好興奮喲。安頓好之後，咦，成架機都無咩人，差不多每個人都是一人霸佔三個位，開頭我都不好意思霸佔三個位，後來我見大家都霸佔三個位，所以...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155037_1e059443de9d2304d7b4a733436c11d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155037_1e059443de9d2304d7b4a733436c11d1.jpg&h=fe8b6d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機方面，好好味，由其是沙津，我食過最好味的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155326_38478f5b304e467274671811ae3d9a35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155326_38478f5b304e467274671811ae3d9a35.jpg&h=59a61c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155340_2d8c6a1bc96d37f98c42694c6e95f68a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155340_2d8c6a1bc96d37f98c42694c6e95f68a.jpg&h=f34e43df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實說，我搭過咁多次（1次，計埋來回4次）長途機，都未試過睡得咁甜的，一個人霸佔三個位，雖然好似蝗蟲，但如果你放低了這個包袱，其實全機的人都一樣咁訓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155418_ab0f13e51cd2d55e9289519e70614126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155418_ab0f13e51cd2d55e9289519e70614126.jpg&h=113b5c64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155419_85b71829b764cbacd892e429eecbd1a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155419_85b71829b764cbacd892e429eecbd1a3.jpg&h=9f5433c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n訓下訓下，好快就到杜拜了<br />\n好啦我覺得，多哈的機場比較乾淨和土豪，杜拜的比較普通，可能好多人的關係，感覺非常烏煙瘴氣。聽講以前搭阿聯酋航空在杜拜轉機會有免費午餐，出發前做過功課，現在已經沒有了，但我沒有查證。既然沒事可做，我找了張長椅，又睡覺了。<br />\n雖然這裡好似紅磡城際直通車的車站，但長椅真係幾好睡，好快就過四個鐘了。我走到閘口等候，一大堆意大利人等上機，雖然我好喜歡意大利，但說意大利是歐洲的中國準是沒錯，講野大聲是其中一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155457_2ebe8ce2bd48d24c5d7e39f873724d60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155457_2ebe8ce2bd48d24c5d7e39f873724d60.jpg&h=6349fc23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155458_b333879798b629fff2beb0446917e497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155458_b333879798b629fff2beb0446917e497.jpg&h=c9cbcba5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155459_7aadbb275d94c1a93ea0fc4183605169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155459_7aadbb275d94c1a93ea0fc4183605169.jpg&h=fa51e464&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155459_a4bdf5e2f83ba92901867c614f65a059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155459_a4bdf5e2f83ba92901867c614f65a059.jpg&h=d6b4509a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上機了，這次是Boeng 777，還是A380最好坐，今次呢班機非常full，所以要乖乖地就範。<br />\n<br />\n好快，食左個bell，又訓，訓醒食完早餐，又訓好快又到了。<br />\n去之前check左天氣，說米蘭會落雪，因為未看過雪，心裡有點期待，又驚場米蘭打呲會因天氣取消喎，事關第二日就係場比賽了。<br />\n<br />\n好，落機挑戰正式開始。"},{"pid":"10c8a193b775b2c6ca8d938923e957ee86152ba3","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去咗幾耐同洗咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n意大利 十二日<br />\n法國 四日<br />\n萬幾蚊</blockquote>睇場波都千幾蚊<br />\n萬零蚊十幾日<br />\n好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n機票同bnb都唔貴<br />\n我又鐘意行路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5783de74cb73c6f1d2ab55bca85d77e3b25efd","tid":663272,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點買波飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7c0956a3433e673f8af3d57151f5eb4568f0a5","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點買波飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n米蘭官網同viagogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10723f5538ab9d1309a2d4063c29283ab1ebf13c","tid":663272,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93a0872e42f495fe66949643fdfbdd36f9e240f","tid":663272,"uid":179213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T21:22:48.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 六月頭去"},{"pid":"f685309e799dfb513096af43c1e243b0703e2d61","tid":663272,"uid":45164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:38:26.000Z","msg":"有冇話驚俾人偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f64a0ee504f615d204f116e346d745c347191a","tid":663272,"uid":76792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時出文"},{"pid":"6aee4716379520fa871a10dfcfd5010fa1a1db58","tid":663272,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"文呢～"},{"pid":"2fcb85567f60b3d8adcc6aca4cf3d21fd502d945","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T00:34:15.000Z","msg":"（二）<br />\n首先，我想買sim card先，因為我要聯絡房東，要用Google map搵地方，我唔係住喺市區的，我住喺聖西路球場站，向來路痴的我，用地圖出事率都高達80%，唔用一定仆街啦。但..點知屌你機場好多野都未開門，最撚有趣是連案內所都未開，咁我唯有試試不用Google map只靠房東預先給我的資料硬闖。搭機場快線好似就13歐可以喺民宿附近嘅站落車，搭巴士就8歐喺中央火車站落車，好處就係平啲同埋有得買sim卡，但就遠啲。最後我都係博一博去搭機場快線。<br />\n<br />\n往聖西路的途中<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/080241_870094eaec2acd6fcb79df6b6997faac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F080241_870094eaec2acd6fcb79df6b6997faac.jpg&h=1200c2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/080312_7c89f6f6093addea353c52efaa967b01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F080312_7c89f6f6093addea353c52efaa967b01.jpg&h=40b8331f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/080313_1b355ae5d94139d8349b073075e50cef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F080313_1b355ae5d94139d8349b073075e50cef.jpg&h=88d95d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/080313_126b2067ee2161c5c179537ce64f4975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F080313_126b2067ee2161c5c179537ce64f4975.jpg&h=095c0fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/080314_126b2067ee2161c5c179537ce64f4975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F080314_126b2067ee2161c5c179537ce64f4975.jpg&h=fca9f67d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/080314_df0d7294af636284cb4a478236ed4022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F080314_df0d7294af636284cb4a478236ed4022.jpg&h=3233955d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\noh shit 落緊雪，雖然我未見過真係覺得幾靚...但真係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾經辛苦，上左車落左車，去到bnb地點但...咦係喎屌我點聯絡屋主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一條女企撚左喺屋苑門口，成個賊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不知所措，就係呢個時候，我遇到今次喺意大利第一個好人，光頭大哥幫我搵保安，保安話知邊個幫我聯絡左屋主落黎，好彩咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到間屋，都幾大，有露台一間大房開放式廚房一個廁所，我諗如果喺香港呢間屋應該要千幾萬啦，咁我喺到住一晚就三百幾四百港紙，因為佢都比較遠，所以就幾平。<br />\n不過...我到埗都未同到屋企人報到，一心諗住黎到有Wi-Fi點知屋主話Wi-Fi壞撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n焦急嘅我即刻沖去搭巴士去返聖西路站再出去先，點知都唔係話你想即刻就即刻到，我喺雪中等撚左半個鐘先有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/081427_34bb5af80bd00e687e88876ea117d6d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F081427_34bb5af80bd00e687e88876ea117d6d3.jpg&h=487cabc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/081428_015353c5655c9233c7f65fc122e00ae7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F081428_015353c5655c9233c7f65fc122e00ae7.jpg&h=fdaa84ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我好撚肚餓呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於出到去，我去左中央火車站間TIM屌左張SIM卡，好平呀，35歐？有成15gb，加多5歐就有30gb，但我只買了15gb，好蠢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當sim卡插入嘅一刻，我好感動，終於可以同外界聯絡，不過我以為好多人擔心我，原來我諗多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我係時候要醫肚了<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/082403_b500116858c2bcce0f106cbd6e805728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F082403_b500116858c2bcce0f106cbd6e805728.jpg&h=760a881a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢個天才，帶左差電器，竟然無帶線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩侍應哥哥借俾我<br />\n食飽之後<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/082524_532eb53bd11ae6be6a345732b15bc4a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F082524_532eb53bd11ae6be6a345732b15bc4a7.jpg&h=31d8ff3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/082525_9294c42e1b0915ef9480041c5e1910b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F082525_9294c42e1b0915ef9480041c5e1910b2.jpg&h=c73d9c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說，大教堂門口多手繩黨影相黨是常識吧，基本上直行直過就得，但今次黎意大利感覺上多左警察，手繩黨都唔多覺眼，總之大家小心為妙，唔好理啲主動好心幫你買飛嘅人，依家火車站多左好多著制服嘅人教你買飛，唔識問佢地啦⋯⋯<br />\n我之後仲遇到各種死x難打嘅吉卜賽人，之後再講。<br />\n話說，我返到屋企，電話已經得返幾%，呢個時候，我唔記得邊間單位係我住果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我WhatsApp屋主，<br />\n點知<br />\n一WhatsApp完佢電話自己熄左，<br />\n之後我好似台慶抽樓咁，細細聲續間試。<br />\n萬一，有人發現我要點解釋？<br />\n點解試極都唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會唔會俾人拉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/083121_4a2ad679ef690128cac8179e1ba6278d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F083121_4a2ad679ef690128cac8179e1ba6278d.jpg&h=2b3ec679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我重複試，終於<br />\n終於得左啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻差電，好彩我有尿袋，因為原來我帶黎嘅插穌係唔岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我WhatsApp屋主問佢邊到有得買，佢話借俾我，上到黎，佢狂笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢笑我開人地對門笑左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（續）"},{"pid":"08189d83c20b4582c08f7ced67d668ba5aca2916","tid":663272,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"Wow有Bolzano!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b80910f9cc9a9d9b012c3a2c6b6323dc773f97","tid":663272,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"最後viagogo張飛點？"},{"pid":"6aa158259897263231c8e2461406e38c0890e412","tid":663272,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後viagogo張飛點？</blockquote><br />\n開波前兩日寄俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1155026bf2bb586be89b8df09fa8b49d8a98583","tid":663272,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"米蘭打比?<br />\n落雪?<br />\n你去睇取消左果場?"}]}